Package: cart
Type: Package
Title: Diffusion-based cartograms
Version: 0.3.2
Date: 2021-01-14
Author: Thomas Zumbrunn <thomas.zumbrunn@pronatura.ch>
Maintainer: Thomas Zumbrunn <thomas.zumbrunn@pronatura.ch>
Authors@R: c(person("Thomas", "Zumbrunn", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "thomas.zumbrunn@pronatura.ch"), person("David H.", "Brown", role = c("ctb")))
Description: Produce density-equalising maps or "cartograms" based on the
    diffusion-based method by Michael T. Gastner and Mark E. J. Newman and an
    implementation by Mark E. J. Newman
    (http://people.cas.sc.edu/hardistf/cartograms/).
Depends:
    R (>= 3.6.3)
Imports:
    maps (>= 3.3.0),
    maptools (>= 0.9-9),
    sp (>= 1.4-0)
Suggests:
    mapdata,
    graphics
SystemRequirements: fftw3 (http://www.fftw.org)
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://github.com/pronaturabl/cart/
BugReports: https://github.com/pronaturabl/cart/issues
LazyLoad: yes
LazyData: yes
Encoding: UTF-8
Collate:
    'cart.R'
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
